N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 177.13 - Change in approved course of study

State Regulations

There shall be no change or alteration in any approved
course of study of any subject or in any instruction staff without prior
written notice to, and approval by, the department. Notes
